episode_summary: In this episode, Sarah Maslowski shares her journey from teaching to becoming a top real estate agent using YouTube as a primary lead generation tool. She discusses the importance of creating value-driven content that answers potential clients' questions about moving to your area. Sarah provides actionable insights on leveraging YouTube effectively and managing leads, emphasizing the power of consistency and authenticity in content creation.
